1) "bam config"
2) make sure that client builds normally: "bam client_release"
3) clean the native binaries (we'll recompile them as bytecode): "bam client_release -c"
4) install emsdk from https://s3.amazonaws.com/mozilla-games/emscripten/releases/emsdk-portable.tar.gz and activate it (emcc -v should work)
5) ./compile_to_js
6) ????
7) PROFIT
